import axios from "axios"; import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useParams } from "react-router-dom"; function Product_Detail(){ const param = useParams(); const [data,setData] = useState({}); useEffect(()=>{ axios.get("http://localhost:8080/laravel8/laravel8/public/api/product/detail/" + param.id ) .then(res=>{ console.log(res) setData(res.data.data) }) },[]); function renderData(){ if(Object.keys(data).length > 0){ return Object.keys(data).map((key,index)=>{ return(

ZOOM

{data.name}

Web ID: 1089772

US $59

Availability: In Stock

Condition: New

Brand: E-SHOPPER

) }) } } return(
{renderData()}
) } export default Product_Detail;
